Name: ircd_motdonconnect
Author: katsklaw
Category: Other
Last updated: 2008-05-13T01:01:21+01:00

This module \"pushes\" services\' motd file to new users upon connecting to the network.

NOTE: This module does NOT work on networks with os_raw loaded! If you don\'t like it, then too damned bad! I don\'t owe an explanation to anyone as to why. >:(

Version 1.0.1 supports Anope 1.8.3
